Christopher SUTHERLAND , Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-4172 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. November 20, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The mandate in 2D15-1413 having issued October 13, 2016, this petition alleging ineffective assistance of appellate counsel is dismissed as untimely. See Fla. R. App. P. 9.141(d)(5).

KHOUZAM, MORRIS, and LUCAS, JJ., Concur.
